    <lb n="24"/>εἰς οὕσπερ<g type="apostrophe"/> ἦσαν τόπους <g type="mid punctus"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">π</unclear>ρὸ τούτου, γράψον ἡμῖν περὶ <expan>τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ού</supplied>τ<ex cert="high">ων</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="25"/>ἀποστέλλων πάραυτα καί τινα <g type="mid punctus"/> τὸν ὀ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">εί</supplied>λ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>τα παρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>λ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αβ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">εῖν</unclear> <expan>αὐτοὺ<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="26"/>τούτους γὰρ<g type="apostrophe"/> κελεύσει θεοῦ <choice><corr>παραδίδομεν</corr><sic>πα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear>αδιδ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>υμεν</sic></choice> αὐτῷ ἐντελῶς. 

    <lb n="27"/>ἐνδρανῶς δὲ καὶ μετὰ πασῆς ἀκριβείας ἐνέχθητι 

